WEBVTT

00:03.086 --> 00:04.254
(chuckles)

00:04.296 --> 00:05.547
Check this out.

00:05.589 --> 00:07.048
What does it say?

00:07.090 --> 00:08.049
Just read it.

00:07.090 --> 00:08.049
It's funny.

00:08.091 --> 00:09.551
I don't read.

00:09.593 --> 00:11.553
Not unless I absolutely

00:09.593 --> 00:11.553
have to for school.

00:11.595 --> 00:13.681
Otherwise, I feel

00:11.595 --> 00:13.681
like they've won.

00:13.722 --> 00:15.641
You never read the paper?

00:15.683 --> 00:17.058
No.

00:17.100 --> 00:18.268
Not even comics?

00:18.310 --> 00:19.520
Like Peanuts?

00:19.561 --> 00:20.896
You never read Peanuts?

00:20.938 --> 00:21.856
Nope.

00:21.897 --> 00:23.064
Are you serious?

00:23.106 --> 00:24.775
You've never read Peanuts?

00:24.817 --> 00:27.068
Uh-uh.

00:32.950 --> 00:34.075
Go ahead.

00:34.117 --> 00:36.119
I promise I'll hold it.

00:38.205 --> 00:42.125
♪ Yes, no, maybe ♪

00:42.167 --> 00:44.336
♪ I don't know ♪

00:44.378 --> 00:47.673
♪ Can you repeat the question? ♪

00:47.715 --> 00:49.967
♪ You're not the boss

00:47.715 --> 00:49.967
of me now ♪

00:50.009 --> 00:52.260
♪ You're not

00:50.009 --> 00:52.260
the boss of me now ♪

